CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Flash Newspicture Magazine, February 14, 1938, pg. 23 reads: "For Her Pittsburgh Admirers Lena sings a farewell ballad to this most appreciative audience during the intermission at the party held in her honor. Picture shows Dr. 'Bus' Cornelius, Charlotte Cattlin [sic] (at the piano), Julia B. Jones, Ada Walker and Walter Rainey."
TitMainTitle: Lena Horne singing, Charlotte Catlin playing piano, and Dr. "Bus" Cornelius, Julia B. Jones, Ada Walker, and Walter Rainey looking on, in Loendi Club
